{"tid":2130572,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【再工業化】政府資助設立智能生產線 尋找新增長點","createTime":"2020-07-29T09:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T10:36:37.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5e68a094371e01f279b3633c3a5afdf797402efb","tid":2130572,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2705000/2707038/202007_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2705000%2F2707038%2F202007_1024.png&h=1949df34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為推動香港再工業化，創新科技署今日（27日）推出「再工業化資助計劃」，資助生產商在香港設立新智能生產線。<br />\n<br />\n所有根據《公司條例》（第622章）在香港成立的公司均符合計劃的申請資格。<br />\n政府會以1（政府）：2（公司）的配對形式提供資助，最高資助額為項目總支出的三分之一或1,500萬元，金額以較低者為準。核准資助金額會在項目完成後發放。<br />\n <br />\n計劃的資助範圍涵蓋與在香港設立新智能生產線直接相關的費用，包括機械、設備或儀器的購置、安裝及投產成本，以及就設計和建立相關生產線而委聘技術顧問的費用等。<br />\n<br />\n該署發言人說，政府在「創新及科技基金」下撥款20億元推行「再工業化資助計劃」，鼓勵生產商在港發展以智能生產為基礎的先進製造業，為本地經濟尋找新增長點。"},{"pid":"56ada4980b2b90540c2b3458a51240cd04303700","tid":2130572,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:42:29.000Z","msg":"又送錢畀中資<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2cd45de00ddeb231af16895163e8bd22ab5bee","tid":2130572,"uid":56698,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:53:39.000Z","msg":"好有信心一定喺益自己人同埋失敗收場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae3e2972f445e439c46ac76a0e62da5f2d68539","tid":2130572,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"唔好話俾人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再工業化係吳永嘉推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳永嘉係工業第二功能界別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係廠商會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d18bf00107b877121c181a03a10ba558199c8b3","tid":2130572,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cae3e2972f445e439c46ac76a0e62da5f2d68539","tid":2130572,"uid":131836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:01:51.000Z","msg":"唔好話俾人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再工業化係吳永嘉推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳永嘉係工業第二功能界別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係廠商會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5918aa7f5e29c06cb0585b8ee69d5fe822cec49b","tid":2130572,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:04:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4330fb6644ca506e0c0e6c439cab796258fea6a5","tid":2130572,"uid":26050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:04:54.000Z","msg":"你睇埋科技園董事會主席係邊個<br />\n<br />\n香港工業總會既查毅超吖"},{"pid":"7daa34849e1f2a703adddd2603dbbfefa4bc6498","tid":2130572,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec2cd45de00ddeb231af16895163e8bd22ab5bee","tid":2130572,"uid":56698,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:53:39.000Z","msg":"好有信心一定喺益自己人同埋失敗收場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:05:26.000Z","msg":"好似銅心咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28877faf965ff412f332a44288d591644b44d77","tid":2130572,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7daa34849e1f2a703adddd2603dbbfefa